Prowl Apps

Push Notification Support for iPhone/iPod touch using Prowl

Currently:
	twitter


1. Download prowlpy from http://github.com/jacobb/prowlpy/tree (or my modification, http://github.com/omgmovieslol/prowlpy/tree/master)
		git clone git://github.com/jacobb/prowlpy.git

2. Download dependencies
		prowly -- need python-httplib2
		prowl-twitter.py -- need python-twitter (apt-get install python-twitter)
		prowl-rss.py -- need python-feedparser (apt-get install python-feedparser)

3. Edit file with your credentials
		apikey -- get/generate from prowl.weks.net

4. Run
		screen or background it
		python prowl-twitter.py & 


